            <div class="box category-box">
                <h2 style="text-align: center;">BMI Categories</h2>
                <ul class="bmi-categories">
                    <li><strong>Underweight:</strong> BMI less than 18.5</li>
                    <li><strong>Normal weight:</strong> BMI 18.5 to 24.9</li>
                    <li><strong>Overweight:</strong> BMI 25.0 to 29.9</li>
                    <li><strong>Obesity:</strong>
                        <ul class="sub-list">
                            <li>Class 1 (Moderate obesity): BMI 30.0 to 34.9</li>
                            <li>Class 2 (Severe obesity): BMI 35.0 to 39.9</li>
                            <li>Class 3 (Very severe or morbid obesity): BMI 40.0 and above</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <p>These categories help assess potential health risks associated with weight...</p>
            </div>


